data.description: Beautiful 2 story country home perched on the hill with 20 acres m/l. Gorgeous entrance with formal kitchen and vaulted ceilings thru out the house.  Beautiful custom built kitchen cabinets with open floor concept to living room. Master bedroom is oversized with tons of living space. Master bath has jacuzzi tub, double sinks, and separate shower. There is a spacious bonus room upstairs that would make a perfect man cave or additional bedroom. Property has a large pond and a gorgeous view.  Back porch has big spacious seating area for entertaining or just enjoying the sunset.  There's a barn on the property as well as a beautiful garden and garden shed with white picket fence. Two car garage with built in storage that is insulted.  This property is an absolute must see!
